OL,3,CMourners attend funeral of Hefin David
OL,4,Cafter politician's sudden death
OL,6,FThe First Minister Eluned Morgan MS
OL,7,Fwas among those who attended the
OL,8,Ffuneral on Monday (1 September) of the
OL,9,FLabour politician Hefin David, after
OL,10,Fhis sudden death last month.
OL,12,FThe Member of the Senedd for
OL,13,FCaerphilly was found dead at his home
OL,14,Fon 12 August - the day before his 48th
OL,15,Fbirthday.
OL,17,FTributes have previously been paid by
OL,18,Fthose across the political spectrum
OL,19,Fand his family, with Mr David being
OL,20,Fdescribed as "much-loved" and a
OL,21,F"devoted father".
