OL,6,FOn the day of his funeral, Welsh
OL,7,FLabour released a statement in memory
OL,8,Fof his service to Wales.
OL,10,FIt read: "Hefin was a proud Welshman,
OL,11,Fdeeply rooted in the valleys and proud
OL,12,Fto represent the community he loved.
OL,13,FHe served with unwavering commitment
OL,14,Fto bring people together to solve
OL,15,Fproblems, always seeking to unite
OL,16,Faround his belief that we achieve more
OL,17,Ftogether than alone - regardless of
OL,18,Fpolitical persuasion.
