OL,3,CMourners attend funeral of Hefin David
OL,4,Cafter politician's sudden death
OL,6,F"He was a strong, well respected voice
OL,7,Fin the Senedd, never hesitating to
OL,8,Fdemand the best for his constituents
OL,9,Fand for Wales, particularly on issues
OL,10,Fsuch as additional learning needs,
OL,11,Festate management charges and
OL,12,Ftransport.
OL,14,F"More than politics, Hefin will be
OL,15,Fremembered as a devoted family man.
OL,16,FHis love for his daughters, his
OL,17,Fpartner Vikki, and his wider family
OL,18,Fshone through in everything he did. To
OL,19,Fthose who knew him, he was not only a
OL,20,Fcolleague but a kind and thoughtful
OL,21,Ffriend.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
