OL,4,Cafter politician's sudden death
OL,6,F"Hefin's passing is a huge loss to
OL,7,FWelsh Labour and to Wales, but his
OL,8,Flegacy of service, principle and
OL,9,Fhumanity will live on."
OL,11,FPolice were called to a report of a
OL,12,Fmedical emergency at an address in
OL,13,FNelson area of Caerphilly at around
OL,14,F6:55pm on 12 August.
OL,16,FGwent Police previously said
OL,17,Fparamedics attended and confirmed that
OL,18,Fthe man had died. Mr David was
OL,19,Fidentified at the scene by his sister.
