OL,4,Cafter politician's sudden death
OL,6,FAn inquest into the serving
OL,7,Fpolitician's death has been opened and
OL,8,Fadjourned, to be held in April next
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Labour politician was first
OL,12,Felected as an MS for Caerphilly in
OL,13,F2016 and re-elected in 2021.
OL,15,FWales' First Minister Eluned Morgan
OL,16,Fsaid he was an "outstanding
OL,17,Fpolitician" and "much-loved member of
OL,18,Fthe Labour family", while Prime
OL,19,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer called Mr
OL,20,FDavid a "powerful voice for the people
OL,21,Fof Wales".
