OL,6,FMr David's family described him as a
OL,7,F"devoted father" and "soulmate" to his
OL,8,Fpartner Vikki Howells - who is the MS
OL,9,Ffor Cynon Valley and minister for
OL,10,Ffurther and higher education in the
OL,11,FWelsh Government.
OL,13,FIn a tribute previously shared by
OL,14,FWelsh Labour, Mr David's family said:
OL,15,F"It is clear from the very many
OL,16,Fmessages we have received that Hefin
OL,17,Fwas widely respected and held in
OL,18,Fgenuine affection by the community he
OL,19,Frepresented, and by those he worked
OL,20,Fwith during his many years of public
OL,21,Fservice.
